  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:0",
      "text": "RenderMan 提供了多个 nodes，可用于随机 texture colouring、file selection，以及随机 orientation/placement。",
      "ascii_letters": 63,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:4",
      "text": "PxrRandomTileManifold",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:9",
      "text": "Spray Can Colored Lids（喷漆罐彩色盖）",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:10",
      "text": "我们先处理 lids，使用一个极其实用的 randomization node：PxrVary。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:11",
      "text": "该 node 接收 base color（或 colored input），并允许 hue、saturation、gamma 以及许多其他 parameters 按 instance 具有随机值。",
      "ascii_letters": 61,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:12",
      "text": "先把 PxrVary 连接到 PxrSurface 的 Diffuse color，并将 Input Color 设置为明亮的 orange。",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:17",
      "text": "Saturation",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:18",
      "text": "Luminance",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:21",
      "text": "我们希望 art-direct PxrVary 随机选择颜色时使用的 color palette。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:22",
      "text": "实现方式是使用 PxrRamp node，在其中设置 ramp colors。我们还需要把 Ramp Type 设置为 Random Object Color。",
      "ascii_letters": 46,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:24",
      "text": "Ramp Type",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:26",
      "text": "Random Object Color 时才会生效。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:31",
      "text": "我们想要 random-colored lids……也确实得到了 random-colored lids。",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:33",
      "text": "Spray Can Labels（喷漆罐标签）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:36",
      "text": "第一个是 PxrMultiTexture node，我们会把所有 maps 加载到每个 filename parameter 中。",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:37",
      "text": "然后，需要一个 PxrRandomTextureManifold node，通过把 PxrMultiTexture files 分配到 cans 上，来控制它们的 randomness。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:40",
      "text": "Number of Textures",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:41",
      "text": "parameter 设置为要使用的 file list 中 textures 的数量。",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:42",
      "text": "PxrRandomTextureManifold 还有各种可调 parameters，可以添加更多 randomization，例如 random texture orientation、flipping、offset 等等，所以 texture randomization 的数量……几乎没有尽头！",
      "ascii_letters": 105,
      "cjk_chars": 27
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:44",
      "text": "这两个 nodes 并不只是用于随机选择 colors 或 diffuse textures。",
      "ascii_letters": 26,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:45",
      "text": "例如，PxrRandomTextureManifold 也可以用于随机分配和变换 roughness/bump maps、叠加 random textures、变换 random edge breakup masks 等。",
      "ascii_letters": 77,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:46",
      "text": "PxrVary 可以为 roughness maps 添加 random color/saturation variation，让每个 instance 拥有不同的 roughness values。同样的 technique 也可用于设置 random bump 和 specular values，以及控制 clear coat 上的 random thickness。",
      "ascii_letters": 130,
      "cjk_chars": 29
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5191b2ddee:48",
      "text": "如果你想在所有 instances 上实现完整的 shading randomization，这两个 nodes 是不错的起点！",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    }
  ],
